channel.title: [PI] Adding Skill
channel.description:
Hey everyone, I downloaded a Blank PI source to hopefully learn something from it and see how far i can get anyways im already stuck on skills....
Im trying to add these... http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/tutorials/302061-pi-fletching-mining-firemaking-fishing-more.html#post2552628
Change the google.org to rune-serba.org (its not that but most of you know :)
I started with flething seeing as that the first skill listed and i get this error after everything is added
[code]src\server\model\players\skills\Fletching.java:158: cannot find symbol symbol : class CycleEvent location: class server.model.players.skills.Fletching CycleEventHandler.getSingleton().addEvent(c, new CycleEvent() { ^ src\server\model\players\skills\Fletching.java:158: cannot find symbol symbol : variable CycleEventHandler location: class server.model.players.skills.Fletching CycleEventHandler.getSingleton().addEvent(c, new CycleEvent() { ^ 2 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Also i looked through the other skills he has done and they all have CycleEventHandler.getSingleton().addEvent(c, new CycleEvent() {
So that would just cause more errors to popup on the same thing
If any one can help me please do so I really badly need this!!
